nodes.description: Fetch content from the provided URL using BrowserAgent.
nodes.agent_prompt: Retrieve the content from the URL: https://www.google.com. Save the raw HTML content to a variable named `raw_html_T001`.

nodes.description: Distill key information from the fetched HTML content.
nodes.agent_prompt: Analyze the provided HTML content (`raw_html_T001`) and extract the main title, meta description, and any prominent text. Structure the extracted information into a clear, concise summary. Save this summary as `distilled_content_T002`.

nodes.description: Format the distilled content for presentation.
nodes.agent_prompt: Format the distilled content (`distilled_content_T002`) into a human-readable markdown string. The output should clearly present the extracted title, meta description, and prominent text. Save the formatted output as `formatted_summary_T003`.
